  "detailed_description": "Put on your helmet and get ready to take action!<br>In PigShip and the Giant Wolf you will help to a little piggy to save his brothers of the claws of the Wolf Army and defeat them. Are you ready for some classic Shoot’em Up action?<br>With online ranking chart to compare your best times with friends and players from all over the world.<br><br>Key Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic arcade with a beautiful pixel art.<br></li><li>6 Stages full of enemies and giant bosses.<br></li><li>3 shooting types.<br></li><li>Ranking online on Bones Mode.<br></li><li>Steam Achievements.<br></li><li>Level up system on Normal Mode.</li></ul>",
